title: #566 - Yoel Romero
description:
Yoel Romero, a former olympian who won the silver medal in the 2000 Olympics as a member of Cuba's wrestling team, and current #1 contender in the UFC's Middleweight division, joins Joey Diaz and Lee Syatt LIVE in studio.
